                  <span class="ncl-stat-label">out of 4,674 teams</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ncl-stat">
                  <span class="ncl-stat-value">121<sup>st</sup></span>
                  <span class="ncl-stat-label">individually (~8,000 competitors)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ncl-stat">
