                  <span class="ncl-stat-label">nationally</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p>
            NCL covers OSINT, network traffic analysis, cryptography, log analysis, password cracking,
            web application exploitation, and forensics. You either solve the challenge or you
            don't&mdash;there's no partial credit for understanding something in theory. Going from
            zero formal background to that result in about a year&mdash;with, admittedly, a seasoning
            of unemployment that gave me an unreasonable amount of free time to pour into
            it&mdash;is probably the most concentrated example of how I tend to approach things when
            something catches my attention.
          </p>

          <div class="cert-row">
            <div class="cert-chip">
